               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-232vc)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 2ra-42rc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     43ra-77vc)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 78ra-113vc)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     114ra-158vc)
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 159ra-201rc)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     202ra-232vc), incomplete
 
 The commemorative notices are followed by
                     ʿarke-hymns.</summary>
