                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is incomplete, the end is missing. The
                           front and back boards are missing. 
 The sewing has been repaired;
                           some fols., especially in quire I, are held in place by crude recent
                           stitches.
 The Ms. is severely worn at the margin, esp. at the
                           beginning and the end, sometimes with the loss of text (e.g., <locus target="#232rb">232rb</locus>).
 Most fols. are affected by
                           humidity; several fols are stained with wax or dirt. The text has been
                           partly damaged on <locus target="#188v">188v</locus>, 221r.
 f. 7 is
                           misplaced: it originally followed <locus target="#227">227</locus>. Some
                           fols. are missing.
 <locus target="#42">42</locus> is half the size
                           of the other fols.
 Holes or tears amended, e.g., on fols. 3, 17, 26,
                           38, 72, 97, 109.</condition>
