                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors; a few lines of
                           the incipit pages of Texts I-1 to I-6, alternating with black lines;
                           incipit of each commemorative notice; the word salām; elements of the
                           punctuation signs, the text dividers and the quire marks; elements of
                           Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
