                        ornamental band; anthropomorphic motifs (faces).</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d2">
                        <locus target="#113vc">113vc</locus>: simple short coloured (red, black,
                        white) ornamental band; geometric motifs.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
