               <provenance>The names of the original donors have mostly
                     been erased or crossed out in the supplication formulas but are still legible
                     on several fols.: Gabra ʾƎgziʾ (e.g., 2rb, 3va,
                     5vc, 6va, 8rab, 9rbc), Walda Rufāʾel (e.g., 18rc,
                     38rc, 41vb), Walatta ʾAragāwi (e.g., 34va, 38rb,
                     41va), Tasfā Giyorgis (e.g., 40ra, 49vc, 75vc).
                     Their names have been replaced in a secondary hand by the names of Sǝbḥāt
                     la-ʾAb (e.g., 11ra, 12vb, 13rbc, 14ra), Walatta
                     Masqal (e.g., 25vc, 27rac, 30ra, 30vbc), Walatta
                     Māryām (e.g., 16vb, 17ra, 18rc, 27va).</provenance></history>
